Hi Kristin.  I find that some of this is very similar to traditional EVP, where more than one 
thing can be heard fairly well in the same example.  It can really make things confusing!  

I often wonder why they can&#39;t be more clear, more often, but then I have to laugh when I 
think about all the song lyrics that get slaughtered by people singing along with the tune 
and then just guessing at what the less clear parts say.  LOL.  :0)

Check out this fun site I ran across (Kiss This Guy:  The Archive of Misheard Lyrics):

http://www.kissthisguy.com/

Margaret

